 dimensional gates did provide certain opportunities.
 For instance, it meant that if he could capture the gates fast enough, he
 could get access straight into the heart of Ibasan operations, perhaps even
 Ulquaan Ibasa itself.
 Destroying the gate in their main base would no doubt utterly cripple the
