 Finally, it opened the possibility of stealing the design from whoever made
 the thing – something he definitely wanted to do if it was at all possible.

\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
Hopefully the design wasn't exclusively held by Quatach-Ichl or ran on
 children's souls or some such, because that was one amazing piece of magic.

